---
// Social proof section with research backing
---

<section class="section relative bg-[#0d0d0f]" id="proof">
  <div class="container">
    <!-- Section Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <span class="text-purple-400 font-medium text-sm uppercase tracking-wider">Built on Science</span>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold mt-4 mb-6" style="font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;">
        Research-Backed Learning
      </h2>
      <p class="text-zinc-400 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Our algorithm is built on decades of cognitive science and motor learning research.
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Research Cards -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-16">
      <div class="glass-card p-6">
        <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-purple-400 mb-2">10M+</div>
        <div class="text-lg font-medium mb-2">Anki Users</div>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm">
          FSRS algorithm powers spaced repetition for millions of medical students, language learners, and professionals.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="glass-card p-6">
        <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-violet-400 mb-2">140+</div>
        <div class="text-lg font-medium mb-2">Years of Research</div>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm">
          From Ebbinghaus (1885) to modern motor learning science â€” our approach is grounded in evidence.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="glass-card p-6">
        <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-blue-400 mb-2">30%</div>
        <div class="text-lg font-medium mb-2">Better Retention</div>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm">
          Studies show spaced repetition improves long-term retention by 30%+ compared to massed practice.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Research Sources -->
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h3 class="text-center text-lg font-medium mb-8 text-zinc-300">Powered by Research From</h3>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
        <div class="text-center p-4">
          <div class="text-zinc-500 text-sm mb-1">Algorithm</div>
          <div class="font-medium text-zinc-300">FSRS</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-zinc-600">Open-source SRS</div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="text-center p-4">
          <div class="text-zinc-500 text-sm mb-1">Motor Learning</div>
          <div class="font-medium text-zinc-300">Schmidt's Schema Theory</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-zinc-600">Variable practice</div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="text-center p-4">
          <div class="text-zinc-500 text-sm mb-1">Skill Stages</div>
          <div class="font-medium text-zinc-300">Fitts & Posner</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-zinc-600">Three stages of learning</div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="text-center p-4">
          <div class="text-zinc-500 text-sm mb-1">Interleaving</div>
          <div class="font-medium text-zinc-300">Shea & Morgan</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-zinc-600">Contextual interference</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Testimonial Placeholder -->
    <div class="mt-16 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <div class="glass-card p-8 text-center relative">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-12 h-12 text-purple-500/20 mx-auto mb-4" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
          <path d="M14.017 21v-7.391c0-5.704 3.731-9.57 8.983-10.609l.995 2.151c-2.432.917-3.995 3.638-3.995 5.849h4v10h-9.983zm-14.017 0v-7.391c0-5.704 3.748-9.57 9-10.609l.996 2.151c-2.433.917-3.996 3.638-3.996 5.849h3.983v10h-9.983z"/>
        </svg>
        <blockquote class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-medium mb-6 text-zinc-200">
          "I've been training for 8 years and always struggled to retain techniques between classes. This approach finally makes sense."
        </blockquote>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-400 to-violet-600"></div>
          <div class="text-left">
            <div class="font-medium">Early Beta Tester</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-zinc-500">Purple Belt, 8 years training</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
